{
  "id": "6a28cae46c947235a9ed678e",
  "title": "二度とやるかと思う事案",
  "created": 1781058277,
  "updated": 1781063632,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a28cae46c947235a9ed678e",
      "text": "二度とやるかと思う事案",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058277,
      "updated": 1781058277
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cae500000000001b0886",
      "text": "from [2026/06/10]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058277,
      "updated": 1781058277
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cae500000000001b0887",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058277,
      "updated": 1781058287
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cae500000000001b0888",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058277,
      "updated": 1781058277
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cae500000000001b0889",
      "text": " 誰かがやらなきゃダメそうなこと X に気づいて X を率先してやったら逆に批判を受けて二度とやるかと思う事案",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058277,
      "updated": 1781058277
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cae500000000001b088a",
      "text": "\tAED の話だっけ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058277,
      "updated": 1781058277
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cae500000000001b088b",
      "text": "\t\tAED しないとその人は助からなさそうだから AED したら、服を脱がせた痴漢扱いされたとか（このエピソード自体ホントか？と思うけど）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058277,
      "updated": 1781058277
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cae500000000001b088c",
      "text": "\tこの構図って元々やりたくてやってるわけじゃない分、物凄い勢いでやる気が削れそう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058277,
      "updated": 1781058277
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cae500000000001b088d",
      "text": "\t\tやりたくてやってるわけじゃない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058277,
      "updated": 1781058277
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cae500000000001b088e",
      "text": " \t\tやれと言われたわけでもない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058277,
      "updated": 1781058277
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cae500000000001b088f",
      "text": " \t\t\t→ 自分の意志でやってはいる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058277,
      "updated": 1781058277
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cae500000000001b0890",
      "text": " \t\tが、やりたい、楽しそう、やってみたいという感覚とは異なる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058277,
      "updated": 1781058277
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cae500000000001b0891",
      "text": " \t\t誰かがやらなきゃいけないというある種の義務感・正義感？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058277,
      "updated": 1781058277
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cae500000000001b0892",
      "text": " \t\t\t[なけなしの義務感]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058277,
      "updated": 1781058277
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cae500000000001b0893",
      "text": " 一発食らうだけで物凄いやる気が削れるから脆弱な状態",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058277,
      "updated": 1781058277
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cae500000000001b0894",
      "text": " \t[心を折る]されるまであと一歩のギリギリの状態",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058277,
      "updated": 1781058277
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cb2400000000001b0898",
      "text": "\t\tこの一発は右ストレートみたいな強烈なものじゃなくてもよくて、息を吹きかけるくらいの細やかな物でもいい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058340,
      "updated": 1781058346
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cb2a00000000001b089a",
      "text": "\t\t\t[吹けば飛ぶような、なけなしの義務感]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058346,
      "updated": 1781058368
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cae500000000001b0895",
      "text": " この構図もっと分けられそう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058277,
      "updated": 1781058277
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28cae500000000001b0896",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1781058277,
      "updated": 1781058277
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28de6f00000000009ad67d",
      "text": "[Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1781063279,
      "updated": 1781063280
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28ddd900000000009ad676",
      "text": "\t割り箸事件だったか、医療の裁判を連想",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1781063130,
      "updated": 1781063283
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28dde600000000009ad678",
      "text": "\tよく知らないので探す",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1781063142,
      "updated": 1781063148
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28ddeb00000000009ad679",
      "text": "\twikipediaだと「杏林大病院割りばし死事件」と表現するのか",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1781063148,
      "updated": 1781063171
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28de0200000000009ad67a",
      "text": "\t通称の方、[割り箸事件]でいいか",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1781063171,
      "updated": 1781063195
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28dddd00000000009ad677",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1781063133,
      "updated": 1781063133
    }
  ]
}